data.description: This warm and welcoming bungalow is a unique masterpiece. It features 2 bedrooms and one full bath that could easily be converted into a 3 bedroom. It is updated and features an immaculately landscaped backyard. Come enjoy the oasis! The backyard has a 16 x 16 barn/shed that is already wired for electricity and it also has a ramp that can be used for motorcycle parking. It also has a fenced in dog park, perfect for a family with a pet. This home is less than 2 miles to the beltline, walking distance to the grocery store, Marta stop, park, and minutes from downtown which makes this the perfect home or investment property. You don't want to miss this golden opportunity to live your dream life in East Point. It is conveniently located near an abundance of dining and shopping options, Tyler Perry Studios, Midtown, Woodward Academy and the Mercedes Benz Stadium. Less than a block away, you can take a stroll along East Point's TRAIL over to Sumner Park (lighted tennis court avail), watch bike races at the Dick Lane Velodrome, and socialize your pup at the Dog Park. Schedule a viewing today and seize this remarkable opportunity to own a stunning bungalow.     This home qualifies for 100% financing with Cadence Bank.     All items and furniture to remain in home with full price offer. Seller is willing to contribute $2500 towards closing costs or add a door to the office.
